%%{init: {'theme':'dark', 'themeVariables': {'fontFamily':'monospace','fontSize':'15px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant S as Sub-queue<br/>(USDC)
    participant M as REXPrimary<br/>matching
    participant D as Redeem-queue<br/>(wRWA)
    participant O as NavOracle
    participant H as Bridge + Pruv leg

    M->>O: nav()
    O-->>M: NAV
    M->>S: subTotal = tổng USDC muốn vào
    M->>D: redeemValue = tổng wRWA muốn ra @ NAV
    Note over M: matched = min(subTotal, redeemValue)
    Note over M: match P2P - wRWA (redeemer sang subscriber), USDC (subscriber sang redeemer)
    Note over M: 🔒 giả định chuyển token thật, không mint share (chờ David, T2.2)

    alt netSub dương (sub thắng)
        M->>H: bridge (subTotal - matched) USDC sang Pruv deposit
        H-->>M: wRWA về, chia thêm cho subscriber
    else netRedeem dương (redeem thắng)
        M->>H: bridge (redeemValue - matched) wRWA sang Pruv redeem
        H-->>M: USDC về, chia thêm cho redeemer
    else khớp đúng
        Note over M: no-op tới Pruv, chỉ P2P (vẫn emit event)
    end
